{"tid":1370702,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲好著重皮膚護理？","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T19:48:16.000Z","uid":146214,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"213589f07ca0c4dbcdb9d057cad80d787c53e74a","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n小弟係一個皮膚好差嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個嗰陣唔太著重個人衛生。但係越黎大，越著重自己外表，望到自己皮膚真係想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又多痘印又盛<br />\n平時睇Youtube片見到啲美顔youtuber又白又滑真係又妒忌又羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想知道各位巴絲有無護理皮膚嘅好方法/產品推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為自己試過好多唔同方法都無改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望各位巴絲可以比意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS:油性肌膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14c541eb8dd7f9c84f81cfddf0b2f399281918e","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657ef819180dd9a42cf292b29d39f4b5c00f8026","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50550f0e90845e40ffb4109a5a4e070e3cd3424","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"委任証吖唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/di