唔多想去睇醫生<br />\n想儘量用護膚品/生活模式去改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我咁樣諗係咪太天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48ef6d68f48820c7a581bc9f32d579d0369be3c","tid":1370702,"uid":127244,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"635efa8609dfe17168811912dc0f360f50bf1662","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"請求各位巴絲分享一下你哋嘅護膚心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"依度都幾多美容雞留言老點你去啲濕鳩美容中心俾人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開口埋口話出去做facial嗰啲先最撚戇鳩，咪理佢地<br />\n<br />\n我就用開依個brand, 夠晒出名如果冇認識就唔好出去亂咁買其他9流品牌，包裝一流都喺吸引我嘅一大原因之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我係混合性肌膚用咗六年皮膚keep得好好<br />\n用咗咁多年基本上由頭到腳牙膏香水香薰油連狗狗沖涼液都係買佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aesop.com/hk/en/c/skin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aesop.com%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fc%2Fskin&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=747f62bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aesop.com/hk/en/c/skin</a><br />\n你上佢個網睇，再選擇自己皮膚類型就見到有護膚去角質保濕精華液全部詳細列晒出嚟<br />\n方便你跟住佢就咁執齊一套唔使煩<br />\n如果真係有需要做Facial treatment 都可以去佢哋海港城中環分店, 呢啲正正常常自己品牌做返收你$1000 90分鐘唔係嗰啲劏客濕鳩美容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ddfe9ce203ef6837cf9490d8fdb33ace24166c","tid":1370702,"uid":127244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213589f07ca0c4dbcdb9d057cad80d787c53e74a","tid":1370702,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n小弟係一個皮膚好差嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個嗰陣唔太著重個人衛生。但係越黎大，越著重自己外表，望到自己皮膚真係